♪ Get out of my way ♪

289
00:15:06.865 --> 00:15:08.217
-♪ or I might shove...
-Nice umbrella.

290
00:15:08.241 --> 00:15:09.719
Thanks. It's an heirloom.

291
00:15:09.743 --> 00:15:11.762
She's joking.
You look like an idiot.

292
